{"tid":1315266,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【反修例】6名媽媽文化博物館外派涼茶 以母愛力撐年輕人：阿媽永遠在你後面","createTime":"2019-07-14T13:15:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T13:52:09.000Z","uid":212626,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ea3d97f22b440017812622b3dbcc0abdc71ec6d1","tid":1315266,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:15:11.000Z","msg":"有網民今日（14日）發起沙田遊行，酷熱天氣情況下仍無阻市民上街，根據天文台顯示，沙田氣溫現時高達30.6度。有6名媽媽在沙田文化博物館門外自發設水站，<span style=\"color: red;\">提供40桶涼茶、36箱寶礦力、18加侖水、幾千張退燒貼，盼用一杯涼茶，令年輕人心頭一暖，別為反修例感絕望而放棄生命。</span><br />\n<br />\n有母親在Fb群組發文，指反修例行動今天由沙田接力，示意遊行人士到沙田文化博物館門外水站補給。她們自稱和理非（「和平、理性、非暴力」），坦言她們一行6位母親需要照顧孩子，「<span style=\"color: red;\">無法衝上前線、未必個個星期出席到集會」，因此希望在今日出一分力</span>，「一邊湊仔，一邊支援」，用一杯涼茶，令年輕人心頭一暖，以另一種方式力撐年輕人。<br />\n<br />\n育有一名<span style=\"color: red;\">2歲女兒</span>的李小姐為發起人之一，她接受訪問時指與女兒幼稚園學校的Whatsapp群組家長因政見不同爭執，於是與志同道合的家長另起爐灶開新的Whatsapp群組，決定走出來以<span style=\"color: red;\">派涼茶支持年輕人。她慨嘆：我哋一班媽媽要湊仔，唔可以企得太前，但都好希望可以做返啲嘢支持後生仔。</span><br />\n<br />\n現場有不少母親義工加入支援派發飲品，陸續有更多涼茶、飲料運抵水站。<br />\n<br />\n這群母親早前在FB貼出感言，期望以愛感動年輕人勿放棄生命：<span style=\"color: red;\">就算你屋企個阿媽藍到爆，我哋呢班阿媽都會撐你！你受傷，我哋會喊！你要人，我哋會喺後邊！你要物資，我哋去搵！你要去死，我哋會抱住你！年輕人不孤單！如果你被打了，痛了，傷了，哭了，我們一齊哭！任何一個崗位都有用！可能勇武睇唔起我哋！但我哋除左反送中同追究黑警，更大一件事係：唔好死！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2400360/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2400360%2F&d=uli%2BLK8ypwQfiBTSi%2FGP91uzyl20%2B4TZ9N3SWLiWM4Y%3D&h=a12f3dd6\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2400360/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57b7ba96f22b2a14bfa32d21e74024d2dfa673f","tid":1315266,"uid":212626,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ydmcBtd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FydmcBtd.jpg&h=c3a73ecf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13aa2f4b2c4e6c4a1e9eed11c4097ac065152057","tid":1315266,"uid":137506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:17:22.000Z","msg":"阿媽有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31b4fd856ff099f57174b26d9f2bfe527a9de569","tid":1315266,"uid":212626,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:18:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pw73H86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPw73H86.jpg&h=3f2d886b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d66f9343f62e60a601f5931f65664af9ca9a29ba","tid":1315266,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:19:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947a1ac0a933c648f13227d81dc1dafeae204735","tid":1315266,"uid":28970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"31b4fd856ff099f57174b26d9f2bfe527a9de569","tid":1315266,"uid":212626,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:18:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pw73H86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPw73H86.jpg&h=3f2d886b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:19:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />靚媽"},{"pid":"9a6989897e4d684d0a67bcbd66317ce48035bad3","tid":1315266,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:19:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b9a7d5f11c4eef3497f89dacd64d764a3e7c99","tid":1315266,"uid":21002,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:20:11.000Z","msg":"點投胎先有咁既阿媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb4367ca429f3252122e2c127f428db4c061c19","tid":1315266,"uid":23169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"